{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Report a loan shark"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/report-loan-shark.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/report-loan-shark"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"936","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Loan sharks are unlicensed moneylenders - if you use or spot one you can report them anonymously in a number of ways","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:13:58+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Loan sharks are illegal moneylenders who often charge very high interest rates - check if a company is licensed and how to report one that isn\u2019t.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>If you spot a loan shark, or have borrowed money from one, you can report them in confidence. </p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Report a loan shark</strong><br />\n0300 555 2222<br />\nMonday to Friday 9am to 5pm  <br />\nText LOAN SHARK and the lender\u2019s details to 60003  <br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#101;&#112;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#097;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#064;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#112;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#115;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#101;&#112;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#097;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#064;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#112;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#115;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Check to see if a lender is licensed</h2>\n\n<p>You can check to see what companies have a licence.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Consumer Credit Register</strong>  <br />\n020 7211 8608<br />\nMonday to Friday 9:30am to 4pm    <br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.crw.gov.uk/pr/Default.aspx\" title=\"Check the Consumer Credit Register\" rel=\"external\">Consumer Credit Register</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Court claims, debt and bankruptcy","id":"https://contentapi